#: ../../content/applications/hr/employees/learning.rst:31
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Course Type`: This field determines the format of the course. The "
"two available options are:"
msgstr "\\ :guilabel:`課程類型`\\ ：此欄位決定課程的格式。兩個可用選項為："

