":guilabel:`Work Permit Expiration Notice Period`: Enter the number "
"of :guilabel:`Days` before a work permit expires, when Odoo notifies the "
"responsible person about the upcoming expiration."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`工作許可證到期通知期間`：輸入工作許可證到期前的\\ :guilabel:`天數"
"`，屆時 Odoo 會通知負責人有關即將到期的事宜。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll.rst:137
msgid ""
":guilabel:`YTD Reset Date`: Enter the date when the :abbr:`YTD (Year To "
