msgid "Headcount report"
msgstr "人員編制報表"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:5
msgid ""
"The *Headcount report* in the **Payroll** app shows the number of employees "
"on payroll and allows headcount comparisons between different periods of "
"time."
msgstr ""
"**薪酬管理**\\ 應用程式中的\\ *人員編制報表*\\ 顯示薪資名冊上的員工人數，並允"
"許比較不同時期的人員編制。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:9
msgid "Create a headcount report"
msgstr "建立人員編制報表"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:11
msgid ""
"Create a headcount report to see the number of employees at a specific time "
"or compare headcounts across periods."
msgstr "建立人員編制報表以查看特定時間的員工人數或比較不同時期的人員編制。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:14
msgid ""
"To create a headcount report, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> "
"Reporting --> Headcount` and click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"若要建立人員編制報表，請前往\\ :menuselection:`薪酬管理應用程式 --> 報表 --> "
"人員編制`\\ 並按一下\\ :guilabel:`新增`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:17
msgid ""
"Report name: generated automatically as `Headcount for (Company Name) on the "
"(YYYY-MM-DD)` and **cannot** be modified."
msgstr ""
"報表名稱：自動產生為「(公司名稱) 於 (YYYY-MM-DD) 的人員編制」，**無法**修改。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:19
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: populated automatically (works in both single and multi-"
"company databases)"
msgstr ":guilabel:`公司`\\ ：自動填入（在單一公司和多公司資料庫中均有效）"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:20
msgid ""
":guilabel:`From`/:guilabel:`To` dates: defaults to current date (from) and "
"blank (to). Adjust these to define the period to analyze."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`從`\\ /\\ :guilabel:`到`\\ 日期：預設為目前日期（從）和空白"
"（到）。調整這些日期以定義要分析的期間。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:None
msgid "A headcount report form filled out for the third quarter of 2025."
msgstr "已填寫 2025 年第三季的人員統計報告表單。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:26
msgid "Next, click :guilabel:`Populate` to generate the report."
msgstr "接下來，按一下\\ :guilabel:`填入`\\ 以產生報告。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:28
msgid ""
"At the top of the form, a :icon:`fa-people` :guilabel:`Employees` smart "
"button appears. Clicking the button displays the total number of employees "
"for the selected period."
msgstr ""
"在表單頂部，會顯示一個\\ :icon:`fa-people`\\ :guilabel:`員工`\\ 智慧按鈕。按"
"一下該按鈕會顯示所選期間的員工總數。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:32
msgid "View all headcount reports"
msgstr "檢視所有人員統計報告"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:34
msgid ""
"See how the company headcount has changed over time by viewing all headcount "
"reports in a list view."
msgstr "透過在清單檢視中檢視所有人員統計報告，查看公司人員數量隨時間的變化。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:36
msgid ""
"To view all headcount reports, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> "
"Reporting --> Headcount`."
msgstr ""
"若要檢視所有人員統計報告，請前往\\ :menuselection:`薪酬管理應用程式 --> 報表 "
"--> 人員統計`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:39
msgid "View employees in a headcount"
msgstr "檢視人員統計中的員工"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:41
msgid ""
"TO get an overall view of employees and their salary impact on the company, "
"view all employee records of a specific headcount report."
msgstr ""
"若要全面了解員工及其對公司薪資的影響，請檢視特定人員統計報告的所有員工記錄。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:44
msgid ""
"To view the employees of a specific headcount report, click the :icon:`fa-"
"people` :guilabel:`Employees` smart button at the top of a headcount report."
msgstr ""
"若要檢視特定人員統計報告的員工，請按一下人員統計報告頂部的\\ :icon:`fa-"
"people`\\ :guilabel:`員工`\\ 智慧按鈕。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:47
msgid ""
"All employees from the headcount appear in a list view, grouped "
"by :guilabel:`Department`."
msgstr "人員統計中的所有員工會以清單檢視顯示，並依\\ :guilabel:`部門`\\ 分組。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:49
msgid ":guilabel:`Employee`: the employee's full name"
msgstr ":guilabel:`員工`：員工的全名"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:50
msgid ":guilabel:`Department`: the department their job position is in"
msgstr ":guilabel:`部門`：其職位所屬的部門"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:51
msgid ":guilabel:`Job Title`: their role"
msgstr ":guilabel:`職稱`：其職務"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:52
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Employer Cost`: how much the company pays the employee each pay-"
"period"
msgstr ":guilabel:`雇主成本`：公司在每個薪資期間支付給員工的金額"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:53
msgid ":guilabel:`Wage on Payroll`: the dollar amount on payroll reports"
msgstr ":guilabel:`薪資單上的薪資`：薪資報表上的金額"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:3
msgid "Pay runs"
msgstr "薪資週期"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:5
msgid ""
"*Pay runs* are used to generate multiple :doc:`payslips <payslips>` at once "
"and process them in a group, rather than create and process individual "
"payslips. This method not only helps the payroll department pay employees in "
"less time, but it also helps keep payslips organized."
msgstr ""
"*薪資週期*\\ 用於一次產生多張\\ :doc:`工資單 <payslips>`\\ 並以群組方式處理，"
"而非建立和處理個別工資單。此方法不僅協助薪酬管理部門在更短時間內支付員工薪"
"資，也有助於保持工資單井然有序。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:9
msgid ""
"Typically, a company's payroll department :ref:`creates a new pay run "
"<payroll/new-pay-run>` for each salary structure, for every pay period "
"(usually weekly, bi-weekly, or monthly). If desired, pay runs can be further "
"organized by department, job position, etc."
msgstr ""
"通常，公司的薪酬管理部門會針對每個薪資結構、每個薪資期間（通常為每週、雙週或"
"每月）\\ :ref:`建立新薪資週期 <payroll/new-pay-run>`。如有需要，薪資週期可進"
"一步依部門、職位等進行組織。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:13
msgid ""
"Once a pay run is made, :ref:`payslips are added to the pay run <payroll/add-"
"payslips>`, then the pay run is processed, and employees are paid."
msgstr ""
"建立薪資週期後，\\ :ref:`將工資單加入薪資週期 <payroll/add-payslips>`，接著處"
"理薪資週期並支付員工薪資。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:17
msgid "View pay runs"
msgstr "檢視薪資週期"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:19
msgid ""
"To view all the pay runs in the database, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Payslips --> Pay Runs` to display all "
"payslip pay runs that have been created. These payslip pay runs are "
"displayed in a list view, grouped by :icon:`oi-group` :guilabel:`Status` "
"(either :guilabel:`Ready`, :guilabel:`Done`, or :guilabel:`Paid`), by "
"default."
msgstr ""
"若要檢視資料庫中的所有薪資週期，請前往\\ :menuselection:`薪酬管理應用程式 --"
"> 工資單 --> 薪資週期`\\ 以顯示所有已建立的工資單薪資週期。這些工資單薪資週期"
"預設以清單檢視顯示，並依\\ :icon:`oi-group`\\ :guilabel:`狀態`\\ "
"（\\ :guilabel:`就緒`、:guilabel:`完成`\\ 或\\ :guilabel:`已付款`）分組。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:24
msgid ""
"Each pay run displays the name, the dates it includes, the number of "
"payslips, and the total :guilabel:`employer cost`, :guilabel:`gross`, "
"and :guilabel:`net` amounts for all payslips."
msgstr ""
"每個薪資週期會顯示名稱、涵蓋日期、工資單數量，以及所有工資單的總"
"\\ :guilabel:`雇主成本`、:guilabel:`毛額`\\ 和\\ :guilabel:`淨額`。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:None
msgid "View displaying all pay runs created."
msgstr "顯示所有已建立薪資週期的檢視。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:33
msgid "Create a new pay run"
msgstr "建立新薪資週期"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:35
msgid ""
"New pay runs can be created from the :ref:`Work Entry <payroll/work-entry-"
"pay-run>`, :ref:`Employee Payslips <payroll/payslips-pay-run>`, or :ref:`Pay "
"Runs <payroll/pay-runs-pay-run>` dashboards."
msgstr ""
"可從\\ :ref:`工作記項 <payroll/work-entry-pay-run>`、:ref:`員工工資單 "
"<payroll/payslips-pay-run>`\\ 或\\ :ref:`薪資週期 <payroll/pay-runs-pay-"
"run>`\\ Dashboard 建立新薪資週期。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:41
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/work_entries.rst:24
msgid "Work entry dashboard"
msgstr "工作記項 Dashboard"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:43
msgid ""
"To create a pay run from the work entry dashboard, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Work Entries --> Work Entries`. The "
"current time period is displayed, with the current day highlighted in yellow."
msgstr ""
"若要從工作記項 Dashboard 建立薪資週期，請前往\\ :menuselection:`薪酬管理應用"
"程式 --> 工作記項 --> 工作記項`。系統會顯示目前時間期間，當天以黃色標示。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:47
msgid ""
"All employees appear in a default Gantt view, with all work entries "
"displayed. If necessary, navigate to the desired time period."
msgstr ""
"所有員工會以預設甘特圖檢視顯示，並顯示所有工作記項。如有必要，請前往所需時間"
"期間。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:50
msgid ""
"Once all :ref:`missing work entries are added <payroll/new-work-entry>` and "
"all :ref:`conflicts are resolved <payroll/conflicts>`, click "
"the :guilabel:`Generate Pay Run` button. The pay run is created for all "
"employees, with a status of :guilabel:`Ready`."
msgstr ""
"當所有\\ :ref:`遺失的工作記項已加入 <payroll/new-work-entry>`\\ 且所有"
"\\ :ref:`衝突已解決 <payroll/conflicts>`\\ 後，按一下\\ :guilabel:`產生薪資週"
"期`\\ 按鈕。系統會為所有員工建立薪資週期，狀態為\\ :guilabel:`就緒`。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:None
msgid "The work entries dashboard with the GeneratePay Runs button visible."
msgstr "工作記項 Dashboard，可見「產生薪資週期」按鈕。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:60
msgid "Employee payslips dashboard"
msgstr "員工工資單 Dashboard"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:62
msgid ""
"To create a pay run from the payslips dashboard, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Payslips --> Payslips`. All payslips for "
"all employees are displayed in a default list view, in chronological order."
msgstr ""
"若要從工資單 Dashboard 建立薪資週期，請前往\\ :menuselection:`薪酬管理應用程"
"式 --> 工資單 --> 工資單`。所有員工的所有工資單會以預設清單檢視依時間順序顯"
"示。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:68
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Pay Run` button and a :guilabel:`New Pay Run` pop-up "
"window loads. Select the :guilabel:`Salary Structure` using the drop-down "
"menu. If no :guilabel:`Salary Structure` is selected, the pay run applies to "
"*all* salary structures. Next, select the :guilabel:`Pay Schedule`, which is "
"*how often* employees are paid. The default options "
"are :guilabel:`year`, :guilabel:`half-"
"year`, :guilabel:`quarter`, :guilabel:`2 "
"months`, :guilabel:`month`, :guilabel:`half-month`, :guilabel:`2 "
"weeks`, :guilabel:`week`, or :guilabel:`day`."
msgstr ""
"按一下\\ :guilabel:`薪資週期`\\ 按鈕，系統會載入\\ :guilabel:`新薪資週期`\\ "
"彈出式視窗。使用下拉式選單選取\\ :guilabel:`薪資結構`。如果未選取"
"\\ :guilabel:`薪資結構`，薪資週期會套用至\\ *所有*\\ 薪資結構。接著，選取"
"\\ :guilabel:`薪資時程`，也就是員工收到薪資的\\ *頻率*。預設選項為"
"\\ :guilabel:`年`、:guilabel:`半年`、:guilabel:`季`、:guilabel:`2 個月"
"`、:guilabel:`月`、:guilabel:`半月`、:guilabel:`2 週`、:guilabel:`週`\\ 或"
"\\ :guilabel:`日`。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:75
msgid ""
"Last, using the calendar selector, set the first day the pay run covers in "
"the first blank :guilabel:`Period` field. The second field is automatically "
"populated based on the selection in the :guilabel:`Pay Schedule` field."
msgstr ""
"最後使用日曆選擇器，在第一個空白的\\ :guilabel:`期間`\\ 欄位中設定薪資週期涵"
"蓋的第一天。第二個欄位會根據\\ :guilabel:`薪資排程`\\ 欄位中的選擇自動填入。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:80
msgid ""
"A company pays its employees every month. To configure the pay run for "
"November, the :guilabel:`Pay Schedule` is set to :guilabel:`month`, and the "
"first :guilabel:`Period` field is set to `Nov 1`. Once entered, the second "
"field is automatically populated with `Nov 30`."
msgstr ""
"公司每月支付員工薪資。要配置 11 月的薪資週期，將\\ :guilabel:`薪資排程`\\ 設"
"定為\\ :guilabel:`月`，並將第一個\\ :guilabel:`期間`\\ 欄位設定為 `Nov 1`。輸"
"入後，第二個欄位會自動填入 `Nov 30`。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:0
msgid "A monthly pay run configured for November."
msgstr "為 11 月配置的每月薪資週期。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:87
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`New Pay Run` pop-up window is configured, "
"click :guilabel:`Continue`, and the pop-up window changes to "
"a :guilabel:`Select Employees` window. All employees who match the "
"parameters set in the :guilabel:`New Pay Run` pop-up window appear in the "
"list. Select the desired employees to add to the pay run, or click the box "
"next to :guilabel:`Employees` to select *all* employees in the list."
msgstr ""
"當\\ :guilabel:`新薪資週期`\\ 彈出視窗配置完成後，按一下\\ :guilabel:`繼續`，"
"彈出視窗會變更為\\ :guilabel:`選擇員工`\\ 視窗。所有符合\\ :guilabel:`新薪資"
"週期`\\ 彈出視窗中設定參數的員工都會出現在清單中。選擇要加入薪資週期的所需員"
"工，或按一下\\ :guilabel:`員工`\\ 旁邊的方框以選擇清單中的*所有*員工。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:None
msgid "The pay run employee selection pop-up window."
msgstr "薪資週期員工選擇彈出視窗。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:96
msgid ""
"Once all desired employees are selected, click :guilabel:`Select`. The pop-"
"up window closes, and the pay run appears on the screen."
msgstr ""
"選擇完所有所需員工後，按一下\\ :guilabel:`選擇`。彈出視窗會關閉，薪資週期會顯"
"示在畫面上。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:102
msgid "Pay runs dashboard"
msgstr "薪資週期 Dashboard"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:104
msgid ""
"To create a pay run from the pay runs dashboard, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Payslips --> Pay Runs`. Click "
"the :guilabel:`New` button and a :guilabel:`New Pay Run` pop-up window loads."
msgstr ""
"要從薪資週期 Dashboard 建立薪資週期，請導覽至\\ :menuselection:`薪酬管理應用"
"程式 --> 工資單 --> 薪資週期`。按一下\\ :guilabel:`新增`\\ 按鈕，會載入"
"\\ :guilabel:`新薪資週期`\\ 彈出視窗。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:108
msgid ""
"Follow the same directions as if creating a :ref:`pay run form the payslips "
"dashboard <payroll/new-pay-run-pop-up>`."
msgstr ""
"遵循與從\\ :ref:`工資單 Dashboard 建立薪資週期 <payroll/new-pay-run-pop-"
"up>`\\ 時相同的指示。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:114
msgid "Add a payslips to a pay run"
msgstr "將工資單加入薪資週期"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:116
msgid ""
"Once a :ref:`pay run has been created <payroll/new-pay-run>`, payslips are "
"added as part of the pay run creation. If needed, additional payslips can be "
"created individually, and added to a pay run after it has been created."
msgstr ""
"一旦\\ :ref:`建立了薪資週期 <payroll/new-pay-run>`，工資單會在建立薪資週期的"
"過程中加入。如有需要，可以單獨建立額外的工資單，並在建立後將其加入薪資週期。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:120
msgid ""
"To add a new payslip, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Payslips --"
"> Payslips`. Click the :guilabel:`New Off-Cycle` button and a "
"blank :guilabel:`Employee Payslips` form loads. :ref:`Configure the payslip "
"form <payroll/new-payslip>`, and ensure the :guilabel:`Pay Run` field is "
"populated."
msgstr ""
"要加入新的工資單，請導覽至\\ :menuselection:`薪酬管理應用程式 --> 工資單 --> "
"工資單`。按一下\\ :guilabel:`新增週期外`\\ 按鈕，會載入空白的\\ :guilabel:`員"
"工工資單`\\ 表單。:ref:`配置工資單表單 <payroll/new-payslip>`，並確保"
"\\ :guilabel:`薪資週期`\\ 欄位已填入。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:125
msgid ""
"Once the form is configured, click :guilabel:`Compute Sheet` to calculate "
"the payslip and add it to the selected pay run."
msgstr ""
"表單配置完成後，按一下\\ :guilabel:`計算表單`\\ 以計算工資單並將其加入所選的"
"薪資週期。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:131
msgid "Process a pay run"
msgstr "處理薪資週期"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:133
msgid ""
"After a :ref:`pay run has been created <payroll/new-pay-run>`, and :ref:`all "
"required payslips have been added <payroll/add-payslips>`, the pay run must "
"then be processed, and employees paid."
msgstr ""
"在\\ :ref:`建立薪資週期 <payroll/new-pay-run>`\\ 並且\\ :ref:`加入所有必要的"
"工資單 <payroll/add-payslips>`\\ 後，接著必須處理薪資週期並支付員工薪資。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:136
msgid ""
"Open the desired pay run by navigating to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> "
"Payslips --> Pay Runs`, and clicking on the desired pay run."
msgstr ""
"導覽至\\ :menuselection:`薪酬管理應用程式 --> 工資單 --> 薪資週期`\\ 並按一下"
"所需的薪資週期，以開啟所需的薪資週期。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:139
msgid ""
"For a pay run to be processed, it must have a status of :guilabel:`Ready`. "
"That means the pay run has been created and payslips have been added, but "
"the payslips have *not* been processed."
msgstr ""
"要處理薪資週期，其狀態必須為\\ :guilabel:`就緒`。這表示薪資週期已建立且已加入"
"工資單，但工資單*尚未*處理。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:142
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Create Draft Entry` button, then click :guilabel:`OK` "
"in the :guilabel:`Confirmation` pop-up window to confirm and create a draft "
"of all the individual payslips in the pay run. After this occurs, the pay "
"run status changes to :guilabel:`Done`, and moves to the corresponding "
"grouping on the :guilabel:`Pay Runs` dashboard."
msgstr ""
"按一下\\ :guilabel:`建立草稿記項`\\ 按鈕，然後在\\ :guilabel:`確認`\\ 彈出視"
"窗中按一下\\ :guilabel:`確定`，以確認並建立薪資週期中所有個別工資單的草稿。完"
"成此操作後，薪資週期狀態會變更為\\ :guilabel:`完成`，並移至\\ :guilabel:`薪資"
"週期` Dashboard 上的對應群組。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:148
msgid ""
"At any time, the pay run needs to be reverted back to a status "
"of :guilabel:`Ready`, click the :guilabel:`Revert` button. This action does "
"**not** remove any payslips that have already been added to the pay run, "
"instead, the status changes back to :guilabel:`Ready`."
msgstr ""
"如需隨時將薪資週期恢復為\\ :guilabel:`就緒`\\ 狀態，請按一下\\ :guilabel:`還"
"原`\\ 按鈕。此操作**不會**移除已加入薪資週期的任何工資單，而是將狀態變更回"
"\\ :guilabel:`就緒`。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:152
msgid ""
"After any desired changes have been made, click :guilabel:`Create Draft "
"Entry` and the pay run status changes to :guilabel:`Done`."
msgstr ""
"完成任何所需的變更後，按一下\\ :guilabel:`建立草稿記項`，薪資週期狀態會變更為"
"\\ :guilabel:`完成`。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:155
msgid ""
"It is important to note, that if any payslips in the pay run have a status "
"of :guilabel:`Paid`, the pay run **cannot** revert to a status "
"of :guilabel:`Ready`."
msgstr ""
"需要注意的是，若薪資執行中的任何工資單狀態為\\ :guilabel:`已支付`\\ ，則該薪"
"資執行**無法**還原為\\ :guilabel:`就緒`\\ 狀態。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:158
msgid ""
"Once the status has changed to :guilabel:`Done`, the payments must be logged "
"in the database. Click the :guilabel:`Payment Report` button, and a pop-up "
"window loads, where the payment report details are entered."
msgstr ""
"狀態變更為\\ :guilabel:`完成`\\ 後，必須在資料庫中記錄付款。按一下"
"\\ :guilabel:`付款報表`\\ 按鈕，會載入彈出視窗，您可在其中輸入付款報表詳細資"
"訊。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:162
msgid ""
"Using the drop-down menu, select the :guilabel:`Export Format` for the "
"payment report. The universal option is :guilabel:`CSV`, while all other "
"available options depend on the installed :doc:`payroll localization "
"<payroll_localizations>`."
msgstr ""
"使用下拉式選單，為付款報表選擇\\ :guilabel:`匯出格式`\\ 。通用選項為"
"\\ :guilabel:`CSV`\\ ，而其他可用選項取決於已安裝的\\ :doc:`薪資本地化 "
"<payroll_localizations>`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:166
msgid ""
"Next, select the :guilabel:`Payment Date` using the calendar selector. This "
"is the date the paychecks are issued."
msgstr ""
"接下來，使用日曆選取器選擇\\ :guilabel:`付款日期`\\ 。這是簽發薪資支票的日"
"期。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:169
msgid ""
"Some :doc:`payroll localizations <payroll_localizations>` cause "
"a :guilabel:`Bank Journal` field to also appear. If visible, select the "
"journal the payslips are logged on, using the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"某些\\ :doc:`薪資本地化 <payroll_localizations>`\\ 會顯示\\ :guilabel:`銀行日"
"記帳`\\ 欄位。若可見，請使用下拉式選單選擇記錄工資單的日記帳。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:172
msgid ""
"Once the pop-up window is configured, click the :guilabel:`Generate` button. "
"The :guilabel:`Payment Report` button changes to a :icon:`fa-"
"download` :guilabel:`Download (filetype)` button. To save a copy of the "
"payment report, click the :icon:`fa-download` :guilabel:`Download "
"(filetype)` button, select the location for the file, then "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"設定好彈出視窗後，按一下\\ :guilabel:`產生`\\ 按鈕。\\ :guilabel:`付款報表"
"`\\ 按鈕會變更為\\ :icon:`fa-download`\\ :guilabel:`下載（檔案類型）`\\ 按"
"鈕。若要儲存付款報表副本，請按一下\\ :icon:`fa-download`\\ :guilabel:`下載"
"（檔案類型）`\\ 按鈕，選擇檔案的位置，然後按一下\\ :guilabel:`儲存`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:178
msgid ""
"If the screen is enlarged beyond a certain amount, the :icon:`fa-"
"download` :guilabel:`Download (filetype)` button is hidden from view. In "
"this scenario, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical "
"ellipsis)` icon to view and select the :icon:`fa-"
"download` :guilabel:`Download (filetype)` option."
msgstr ""
"若螢幕放大超過一定程度，\\ :icon:`fa-download`\\ :guilabel:`下載（檔案類型）"
"`\\ 按鈕會從視野中隱藏。在這種情況下，請按一下\\ :icon:`fa-ellipsis-"
"v`\\ :guilabel:`（垂直省略號）`\\ 圖示以檢視並選擇\\ :icon:`fa-"
"download`\\ :guilabel:`下載（檔案類型）`\\ 選項。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:183
msgid ""
"After the report is created, click the :guilabel:`Mark as paid` button to "
"mark the payslips as paid in the database."
msgstr ""
"建立報表後，按一下\\ :guilabel:`標記為已付款`\\ 按鈕，將工資單在資料庫中標記"
"為已付款。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:187
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically creates the name of the pay run according to the various "
"selections made when creating the pay run (salary structure, pay schedule, "
"etc). In some situations, a company may want to rename the pay runs, for "
"better organization and a clearer understanding of what pay slips are part "
"of each pay run."
msgstr ""
"Odoo 會根據建立薪資執行時所做的各種選擇（薪資結構、支付排程等）自動建立薪資執"
"行的名稱。在某些情況下，公司可能希望重新命名薪資執行，以便更好地組織並更清楚"
"地瞭解每次薪資執行包含哪些工資單。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:192
msgid ""
"For example, a company pays its employees monthly, for both hourly and "
"salaried employees."
msgstr "例如，某家公司每月向其時薪和薪資制員工支付薪資。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:194
msgid "The names for their four August 2025 pay runs are:"
msgstr "他們 2025 年 8 月的四次薪資執行名稱為："

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:196
msgid "`Aug 1-14 2025 - Hourly`"
msgstr "`Aug 1-14 2025 - Hourly`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:197
msgid "`Aug 1-14 2025 - Salary`"
msgstr "`Aug 1-14 2025 - Salary`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:198
msgid "`Aug 15-31 2025 - Hourly`"
msgstr "`Aug 15-31 2025 - Hourly`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/pay_runs.rst:199
msgid "`Aug 15-31 2025 - Salary`"
msgstr "`Aug 15-31 2025 - Salary`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:3
msgid "Payroll analysis"
msgstr "薪酬分析"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:5
msgid ""
"The *Payroll Analysis* report displays the total net wage for the company, "
"for the last 365 days. This report allows companies to view their payroll "
"costs and identify any trends."
msgstr ""
"\\ *薪酬分析*\\ 報告顯示公司過去 365 天的總淨工資。此報告讓公司能夠檢視其薪酬"
"成本並識別任何趨勢。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:8
msgid ""
"To view the *Payroll Analysis* report, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll "
"app --> Reporting --> Payroll`."
msgstr ""
"若要檢視\\ *薪酬分析*\\ 報告，請導覽至\\ :menuselection:`薪酬管理應用程式 --"
"> 報表 --> 薪酬管理`。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:11
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Net Wage` is the default metric displayed in the report, but "
"other measures can be displayed if desired, such as *gross wage* or *days of "
"paid time off*. Click the :guilabel:`Measures` :icon:`fa-caret-down` button "
"to view a drop-down menu of other metrics to display. Click on the desired "
"measure to display the results."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`淨工資`\\ 是報告中顯示的預設度量，但如有需要可以顯示其他度量，例如"
"\\ *總工資*\\ 或\\ *支薪休假天數*\\ 。按一下\\ :guilabel:`度量` :icon:`fa-"
"caret-down`\\ 按鈕以檢視其他度量的下拉式選單。按一下所需的度量以顯示結果。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:None
msgid "Payroll overview report showing payroll for the last 365 days."
msgstr "顯示過去 365 天薪酬的薪酬概覽報表。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:22
msgid "View multiple metrics"
msgstr "檢視多個度量"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:24
msgid ""
"It is possible to view multiple metrics at one time by viewing the report in "
"the *pivot table* view. This can aid management to determine other trends, "
"such as which departments do not take time off, or which departments have "
"the highest payroll costs."
msgstr ""
"透過在\\ *樞紐分析表*\\ 檢視中檢視報告，可以同時檢視多個度量。這有助於管理階"
"層確定其他趨勢，例如哪些部門不休假，或哪些部門的薪酬成本最高。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:29
msgid ""
"**Only one** measure is able to be displayed in the default :icon:`fa-area-"
"chart` :guilabel:`Graph` view. Multiple measures are **only** possible in "
"the :icon:`oi-view-pivot` :guilabel:`Pivot` view."
msgstr ""
"**僅有一個**\\ 度量能夠在預設的\\ :icon:`fa-area-chart` :guilabel:`圖表`\\ 檢"
"視中顯示。多個度量\\ **僅**\\ 能在\\ :icon:`oi-view-pivot` :guilabel:`樞紐分"
"析`\\ 檢視中使用。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:33
msgid ""
"To display the data in a pivot table, click on the :icon:`oi-view-"
"pivot` :guilabel:`Pivot` button."
msgstr ""
"若要在樞紐分析表中顯示資料，請按一下\\ :icon:`oi-view-pivot` :guilabel:`樞紐"
"分析`\\ 按鈕。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:35
msgid ""
"The default information displayed includes the number of payslips "
"(:guilabel:`# Payslip`), the number of :guilabel:`Days of Paid Time Off` "
"and :guilabel:`Days of Unpaid Time Off`, along with the :guilabel:`Net Wage` "
"and :guilabel:`Gross Wage`. All the information is organized by department."
msgstr ""
"預設顯示的資訊包括工資單數量（:guilabel:`# Payslip`）、:guilabel:`支薪休假天"
"數`\\ 和\\ :guilabel:`無薪休假天數`，以及\\ :guilabel:`淨工資`\\ 和"
"\\ :guilabel:`總工資`。所有資訊均按部門組織。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:39
msgid ""
"To display more information on the report, click "
"the :guilabel:`Measures` :icon:`fa-caret-down` button to reveal a drop-down "
"menu. Click on any metric to display it on the pivot table."
msgstr ""
"若要在報告上顯示更多資訊，請按一下\\ :guilabel:`度量` :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down`\\ 按鈕以顯示下拉式選單。按一下任何度量以在樞紐分析表上顯示。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:None
msgid "Pivot table view with the various metrics on display."
msgstr "樞紐分析表檢視，顯示各種度量。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:46
msgid "Use case: comparing payroll costs"
msgstr "使用案例：比較薪酬成本"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:48
msgid ""
"Managers can compare payroll costs, and determine which departments have "
"raised their payroll costs, either by hiring more employees, or by raising "
"salaries."
msgstr ""
"管理者可以比較薪酬成本，並確定哪些部門提高了薪酬成本，可能是透過僱用更多員工"
"或提高薪資。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:51
msgid ""
"To compare previous periods of time, first view the *Payroll Analysis* "
"report in a :ref:`pivot table <payroll_analysis/multiple>`. Then, click "
"the :icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`(Toggle Search Panel)` icon in the "
"search bar, and click  :guilabel:`Start Date` :icon:`fa-caret-down` to "
"reveal a list of time periods (months, quarters, and years). Click on a "
"desired time period, and a :icon:`fa-adjust` :guilabel:`Comparison` section "
"appears in the search bar. Click on one of the two available options, "
"either :guilabel:`Start Date: Previous Period`, or :guilabel:`Start Date: "
"Previous Year`."
msgstr ""
"若要比較先前的時間段，請先在\\ :ref:`樞紐分析表 <payroll_analysis/"
"multiple>`\\ 中檢視\\ *薪酬分析*\\ 報告。然後，按一下搜尋列中的\\ :icon:`fa-"
"caret-down` :guilabel:`（切換搜尋面板）`\\ 圖示，並按一下\\ :guilabel:`開始日"
"期` :icon:`fa-caret-down`\\ 以顯示時間段清單（月、季和年）。按一下所需的時間"
"段，搜尋列中會出現一個\\ :icon:`fa-adjust` :guilabel:`比較`\\ 區段。按一下兩"
"個可用選項之一，即\\ :guilabel:`開始日期：上一期間`\\ 或\\ :guilabel:`開始日"
"期：去年`。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:59
msgid ""
"The report now displays three columns of information for every displayed "
"measure: a column for the current time period, a column for the previous "
"time period, and a :guilabel:`Variation` column, which displays the "
"difference between the two time periods in a color-coded percentage (green "
"for increases, red for decreases.)"
msgstr ""
"報告現在為每個顯示的度量顯示三欄資訊：當前時間段的欄、上一時間段的欄，以及一"
"個\\ :guilabel:`變化`\\ 欄，該欄以顏色編碼的百分比顯示兩個時間段之間的差異"
"（綠色表示增加，紅色表示減少）。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:65
msgid ""
"In this example, the data shows an overall increase in the number of "
"payslips. Since the company pays all employees every two weeks, an increase "
"in the number of payslips (:guilabel:`# Payslips`) means that more employees "
"were hired, in this example, a 500% increase."
msgstr ""
"在此範例中，資料顯示工資單數量整體增加。由於公司每兩週向所有員工支付一次薪"
"資，工資單數量（:guilabel:`# Payslips`）的增加意味著僱用了更多員工，在此範例"
"中增加了 500%。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:69
msgid ""
"Additionally, both the :guilabel:`Net Wage` and :guilabel:`Gross Wage` "
"increased. The department :guilabel:`RD US` showed the largest growth, with "
"both metrics increasing by approximately 350%."
msgstr ""
"此外，:guilabel:`淨工資`\\ 和\\ :guilabel:`總工資`\\ 都有所增加。部門"
"\\ :guilabel:`RD US`\\ 顯示了最大的增長，兩個度量均增加了約 350%。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:0
msgid "Pivot table view comparing two years of data."
msgstr "樞紐分析表檢視，比較兩年的資料。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:76
msgid ":doc:`../../essentials/reporting`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../essentials/reporting`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:5
msgid "Payroll localizations"
msgstr "薪資在地化"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:10
msgid ""
"*Payroll localizations* refer to the specific process of adapting payroll "
"systems, policies, and compliance measures to align with the specific labor "
"laws, tax regulations, and social security requirements of a particular "
"country or region."
msgstr ""
"*薪資在地化*是指調整薪資系統、政策和合規措施的特定流程，以符合特定國家或地區"
"的勞動法、稅務法規和社會保障要求。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:14
msgid ""
"This ensures that employee salaries, benefits, deductions, and contributions "
"are processed accurately and in full compliance with local legal and "
"financial obligations."
msgstr ""
"這可確保員工的薪資、福利、扣除額和繳費金額能準確處理，並完全符合當地的法律和"
"財務義務。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:17
msgid ""
"Localization also includes integrating country-specific payroll elements "
"such as benefits, holidays, termination rules, and reporting requirements, "
"helping businesses avoid legal risks while ensuring employees receive their "
"correct compensation."
msgstr ""
"在地化還包括整合國家/地區特定的薪資要素，例如福利、假期、離職規定和報表要求，"
"協助企業避免法律風險，同時確保員工獲得正確的報酬。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:22
msgid "Install localization package"
msgstr "安裝本地化套件"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:24
msgid ""
"A country-specific localization module :ref:`must be installed <general/"
"install>` to properly configure and process payroll. To install the required "
"module, first open the **Apps** app."
msgstr ""
"必須\\ :ref:`安裝 <general/install>`\\ 特定國家/地區的本地化模組，才能正確配"
"置和處理薪酬管理。若要安裝所需模組，請先開啟\\ **應用程式**\\ 應用程式。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:27
msgid ""
"Clear out the default :icon:`fa-filter` :guilabel:`Apps` filter, then type "
"the name of the desired country into the search bar. All available modules "
"for that country are presented."
msgstr ""
"清除預設的\\ :icon:`fa-filter`\\ :guilabel:`應用程式`\\ 篩選器，然後在搜尋欄"
"中輸入所需國家/地區的名稱。該國家/地區所有可用的模組就會顯示出來。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:31
msgid ""
"Some countries only have one localization module, while other have multiple "
"modules. This is typically when other software is neede to process payroll, "
"and importing and exporting data is required."
msgstr ""
"有些國家/地區只有一個本地化模組，而其他國家/地區則有多個模組。這通常是在需要"
"其他軟體來處理薪酬管理，並且需要匯入和匯出資料時才會出現。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:35
msgid ""
"For example. when searching for **Payroll** modules for `Egypt`, the "
"following modules appear in the search, and must be installed: `Egypt - "
"Payroll` and `Egypt - Payroll with Accounting`."
msgstr ""
"例如，搜尋 `埃及` 的\\ **薪酬管理**\\ 模組時，搜尋結果中會出現以下模組，且必"
"須安裝：`Egypt - Payroll` 和 `Egypt - Payroll with Accounting`。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:38
msgid ""
"Refer to the :ref:`country-specific documentation <payroll_localizations/"
"countries-list>` for a complete list of the related **Payroll** modules "
"required for each specific country."
msgstr ""
"請參閱\\ :ref:`特定國家/地區使用說明 <payroll_localizations/countries-"
"list>`，以取得每個特定國家/地區所需的相關\\ **薪酬管理**\\ 模組的完整清單。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:42
msgid ""
"To see if any localization modules have been installed on the database, "
"navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Configuration --> Settings`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Settings` page, if a localization module was installed, "
"a :guilabel:`(Country) Localization` section appears."
msgstr ""
"若要查看資料庫中是否已安裝任何本地化模組，請前往\\ :menuselection:`薪酬管理應"
"用程式 --> 配置 --> 設定`。在\\ :guilabel:`設定`\\ 頁面中，如果已安裝本地化模"
"組，就會出現\\ :guilabel:`（國家/地區）本地化`\\ 區段。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:47
msgid ""
"It is **not** recommended to alter the localization settings, unless "
"specifically required."
msgstr "**不**\\ 建議變更本地化設定，除非有特別需要。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:50
msgid ""
"Odoo can handle a multi-company configuration. This is generally done when "
"there is a main company or office location, such as a headquarters, and "
"there are other offices/branches around the country or globe, that fall "
"under that main company or headquarters. In Odoo, each company, including "
"the headquarters, must be set up as their own company/branch using the multi-"
"company method."
msgstr ""
"Odoo 可以處理多公司配置。這通常是在有一個主要公司或辦公地點（例如總部），並且"
"在該國家/地區或全球各地還有其他辦公室/分支機構隸屬於該主要公司或總部時才會採"
"用。在 Odoo 中，每個公司（包括總部）都必須使用多公司方法設定為自己的公司/分支"
"機構。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:56
msgid ""
"Each individual company can have a different localization setting, since "
"locations can vary anywhere in the world, where rules and laws differ."
msgstr ""
"每個單獨的公司都可以有不同的本地化設定，因為地點可能遍佈世界各地，各地的規則"
"和法律都不同。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:59
msgid ""
"For more information on companies, refer to the :doc:`Companies <../../"
"general/companies>` documentation, which covers how to set up companies."
msgstr ""
"有關公司的更多資訊，請參閱\\ :doc:`公司 <../../general/companies>`\\ 使用說"
"明，其中涵蓋如何設定公司。"

