"structure type and the Thirteen Month salary structure. You can also filter "
"eligible employees by department and / or job position."
msgstr ""
"然後按一下\\ **產生工資單**\\ 按鈕，選取 CP200 薪資結構類型和第十三個月薪資結"
"構。您也可以依部門和/或職位篩選符合資格的員工。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:None
