"的合約、工作時間比例及適用稅款。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:1448
msgid "Calculation of the thirteenth-month salary"
msgstr "十三個月薪資的計算"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:1451
