msgid ""
"Both full-time and part-time employees are eligible, with prorated "
"calculations based on work time."
msgstr "全職和兼職員工均符合資格，根據工作時間按比例計算。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:1458
