#~ "Odoo supports 11 work specific HK work entry types which are used "
#~ "together with the **Time Off** app:"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Odoo 支援 11 種香港適用的工作記項類型，這些類型可與 **休假** 應用程式一起"
