#~ msgid ""
#~ "Odoo allows multiple MPF scheme configurations (currently 24 schemes), "
#~ "creation of new schemes, different MPF groups and member classes, and "
#~ "definition of income for automated MPF calculations. In alignment with "
#~ "eMPF requirements, Odoo-generated eMPF contribution reports are ready to "
#~ "upload to the `eMPF portal <https://www.empf.org.hk/?language_id=1>`_."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Odoo 支援多種強積金計劃配置（目前有 24 個計劃），也可用作建立新的計劃、不"
