#~ msgid ""
#~ "**Jan**: Generate a payslip with a monthly wage of $20200. The :abbr:`ADW "
#~ "(Average Daily Wage)` is always computed on a cumulative basis of the "
#~ "trailing 12-months."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "**一月** ：產生一張月薪為 $20,200 的工資單。每日平均工資是以過去 12 個月的"
#~ "累積值去計算。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "**Feb**: Generate a similar payslip, but add an :guilabel:`Other Input "
#~ "Type` for the :guilabel:`Commission`."
