#~ "**二月** ：產生另一張類似的工資單，但加入一項 :guilabel:`佣金` "
#~ "的 :guilabel:`其他輸入類型`。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "**Mar**: Apply for **one** full-paid annual leave in March. The salary "
#~ "compensation for the leave taken is based on :abbr:`ADW (Average Daily "
#~ "Wage)` thus far."
